LOAD  I, 0
STORE I
LOOP: LOAD  I
      SUB   N
      BGEZ  DONE
      LOAD  I
      BNZ   CHECK
      LOAD  I
      ADD   ONE
      STORE I
      BRA   LOOP
CHECK: LOAD ARR+I
      SUB   ARR+I-1
      BGEZ  ADVANCE
      LOAD  ARR+I
      XCHG  ARR+I-1
      LOAD  I
      SUB   ONE
      STORE I
      BRA   LOOP
ADVANCE: LOAD I
         ADD  ONE
         STORE I
         BRA  LOOP
DONE: HALT
